name: Movimento dos Quartos
query:
SELECT
name as "Registo N:data:120",
tipo_quarto as "Tipo de Quarto:data:100",
preco as "Preco:Currency:100",
hora_entrada as "Hora Entrada:datetime:120",
hora_saida as "Hora Saida:datetime:120",
horas as "Horas:data:30",
total as "Total:Currency:100",
pagamento_por as "Pagamento por:data:100",
status_quarto as "Status:data:100",
total_servicos as "Total Servicos:Currency:100",
servico_pago_por as "Servicos Pagos por:data:100",
reserva_numero as "Reserva N:data:100"

FROM `tabGestao de Quartos`;
